Formally, their refusal to participate in hostilities in Ukraine, the rebel contractors argue that this is not provided for in their contracts.

At the same time, according to our sources, the real reason that makes the Russian military risk criminal prosecution by the authorities is fear. Employees of the occupation army are really shocked by the professionalism of the Armed Forces of Ukraine and the huge losses in equipment and manpower that Ukrainian soldiers have already inflicted on the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation and other security units that Russia has sent to Ukraine.

